txt.en: Deliver the pies to the doorsteps of your neighbors within the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads.

'One of our neighbours just baked some fresh pies for us! I think we should deliver them to some of our other neighbours. What a wonderful surprise to find a fresh pie on your doorstep in the morning!'
When neighbours work together, the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads will shine bright as the beacons.
Fresh pies can be found in the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads.\n\nYou should gather the pies.
